data.description: Wonderful, Spacious Ranch style brick home Conveniently location to shopping, restaurants, Hospitals & schools; Home offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 full Baths, Open concept Eat-in Kitchen and Living Room, large laundry room, covered patio to the beautiful inground pool that offers a great space for entertaining and enjoying warm summer days, Detached Building for extra storage, attached garage and mature landscaping. Seller will provide the purchaser a Choice Ultimate 1yr Choice Home Warranty with pool/spa coverage at closing.
